title: Back office service providers for credit institutions bundle their offer with Dentons (Dentons US LLP) ...
text: ( Source : Dentons US LLP ) September 4 , 2015 Dentons has advised Landesbank Berlin Holding AG and HASPA Finanzholding on antitrust law matters in connection with the planned combination of S-Servicepartner GmbH and NRS Norddeutsche
